Under `mshadow`, `mshadow/extension/implicit_gemm.h` L70-71,

```c++
    const size_t packetSize = Packet::Size();
    DType lhs_temp[packetSize], rhs_temp[packetSize];
```

The 2nd line is allowed by GCC/Clang but not by MSVC for the uncertain array length. Do you want me to do a PR in `mshadow` to fix this?
